### ack configuration file

### Options

# smartcase matching, like in Vim
--smart-case

# sort files
--sort-files

# page resultes
--pager

# Ignore databases
--ignore-file=ext:db

# Ignore tags files
--ignore-file=match:/tag(s)?/

### File Types

# Markdown
--type-set=md=.md
--type-set=md=.markdown
--type-add=md=.mkd
